Ke wa fiɛɛ kpɔmi nɔ́ ɔ he sane kpakpa a kɛ tsɔɔ nihi ɔ , ngɛ mɛni blɔ nɔ lɔ ɔ tsɔɔ kaa wa ngɛ Mawu dloomi ɔ he sane kpakpa a fiɛɛe ?
